title: 2017 First Quarter Power Poll
itunes:title: 2017 First Quarter Power Poll
description:
A room filled with heroes-Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Colleen Wolfe & Gregg Rosenthal recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Andrew Luck starting to practice and Mitch Trubisky (11;57) starting as quarterback for the Bears. The heroes rank all 32 teams in the league in the ATN Power Poll (35;44) and The Subreddit Super Contest continues! (50;12) Is the third time a charm?
